Musio: So, user, do you like computers?

User: Yeah, I love them! My favorite thing to do is play games on them.

Musio: What kind of games do you like to play?

User: I like all kinds of games. My favorites are the ones where you have to solve puzzles or figure out clues to get to the next level.

Musio: That sounds like a lot of fun. Do you think you would like to work with computers when you grow up?

User: Yeah, I think that would be really cool. I want to be a game designer when I grow up.

Musio: That sounds like an excellent career choice. I'm sure you'll be great at it.